04:28.790 --> 04:30.400
♪ Here I am

04:31.314 --> 04:35.275
♪ Rock you like a hurricane!

04:36.363 --> 04:38.103
[music stops]

04:38.147 --> 04:40.323
[rumbling,
electrical crackling]

04:44.066 --> 04:46.808
Okay, okay, enough. Stop.

04:46.851 --> 04:50.072
You're harshing the vibe we
worked very hard to build to.

04:50.115 --> 04:52.422
Oh, but by the end
of my world tour,

04:52.466 --> 04:54.729
we're all gonna have
the same vibe.

04:54.772 --> 04:58.167
We're all gonna be one nation
of Trolls, under rock.

04:58.210 --> 05:00.387
[plays loud chord]

05:03.259 --> 05:04.869
Who's ready to rock?!

05:04.913 --> 05:07.132
